have any Heart-Binding Poison?

00:03:02.260 --> 00:03:03.620
Yes, I do.

00:03:03.870 --> 00:03:05.000
But it took me 10 years

00:03:05.000 --> 00:03:07.270
to cultivate this venomous worm
with blood essence.

00:03:07.270 --> 00:03:08.650
If you need it now,

00:03:08.680 --> 00:03:10.240
there isn't enough time.

00:03:10.750 --> 00:03:12.300
Well, is there any way

00:03:12.330 --> 00:03:13.820
to cultivate it within a day?

00:03:13.820 --> 00:03:14.750
That's not okay.

00:03:14.790 --> 00:03:16.680
In that way, it would accelerate
the depletion of your body.

00:03:16.680 --> 00:03:18.370
The consequences would be unimaginable.

00:03:18.370 --> 00:03:19.490
So you mean

00:03:19.520 --> 00:03:20.780
there is such a method?

00:03:20.930 --> 00:03:21.940
Sang Li, no matter what,

00:03:21.940 --> 00:03:23.340
I must give it a try.

00:03:24.060 --> 00:03:25.070
Sang Li.

00:03:25.550 --> 00:03:27.160
Tell me honestly,

00:03:27.560 --> 00:03:28.930
with my current health,

00:03:29.590 --> 00:03:31.390
how much longer I can stay alive.

00:03:32.079 --> 00:03:33.790
You're like a lamp running out of its oil.

00:03:33.790 --> 00:03:35.650
You may die within these few days.

00:03:37.740 --> 00:03:40.340
I thought
I could stay alive for a few more days.

00:03:40.530 --> 00:03:41.450
Sang Li.

00:03:42.230 --> 00:03:43.420
Regarding this matter,

00:03:43.420 --> 00:03:45.350
please don't tell Jun Che about it.

00:03:45.860 --> 00:03:47.930
I'm afraid if he knows I'm dying,

00:03:48.290 --> 00:03:49.880
he'll definitely go crazy again.

00:03:49.880 --> 00:03:51.440
Even if I don't tell him now,

00:03:51.470 --> 00:03:53.000
he would still go crazy.

00:03:53.230 --> 00:03:54.600
As soon as you pass away,

00:03:54.670 --> 00:03:56.600
he would die with you immediately.

00:03:58.840 --> 00:04:00.720
I have a way to ensure that

00:04:00.740 --> 00:04:02.090
after I pass away,

00:04:02.120 --> 00:04:03.920
he will no longer go crazy again.

00:04:05.300 --> 00:04:07.660
Sang Li, please trust me one more time.

00:04:08.040 --> 00:04:09.000
At this point,

00:04:09.130 --> 00:04:11.660
no matter what you ask for,
I'll say yes to you.

00:04:17.480 --> 00:04:18.579
Sang Li.

00:04:19.730 --> 00:04:22.130
My brother
has a straightforward personality

00:04:22.130 --> 00:04:23.650
and is inarticulate.

00:04:23.680 --> 00:04:25.880
But he is a very good person.

00:04:30.500 --> 00:04:31.780
Thank you, Your Grace.

00:04:35.159 --> 00:04:35.960
Your Majesty.

00:04:36.050 --> 00:04:37.880
Her Grace is not seriously ill.

00:04:37.900 --> 00:04:39.630
She just needs to rest quietly.

00:04:40.659 --> 00:04:41.460
Yingying.

00:04:47.590 --> 00:04:49.159
What's wrong, Your Majesty?

00:04:49.159 --> 00:04:50.690
Don't call me Your Majesty.

00:04:50.790 --> 00:04:51.790
Call me Five.

00:04:53.060 --> 00:04:54.370
Well, Five,

00:04:54.620 --> 00:04:55.690
what's wrong?

00:04:56.140 --> 00:04:58.440
Just now, Sang Li insisted
that I should go out.

00:04:58.440 --> 00:05:00.870
I thought
something bad had happened to you.

00:05:00.870 --> 00:05:03.090
Fortunately, you're not seriously ill.

00:05:03.090 --> 00:05:05.460
If there had been bad news,

00:05:05.480 --> 00:05:06.840
what would you do?

00:05:06.930 --> 00:05:08.590
By searching the whole world,

00:05:08.590 --> 00:05:10.470
I don't believe
I can't find the medicine to cure you.

00:05:10.470 --> 00:05:12.360
What if my fate is just like this,

00:05:12.380 --> 00:05:14.060
and it's hard to defy Heaven's will?

00:05:14.060 --> 00:05:15.790
Then I'll go against Heaven.

00:05:16.330 --> 00:05:17.860
I'll sacrifice my own life.

00:05:18.260 --> 00:05:20.560
If you're gone,
it'll be meaningless for me to stay alive.

00:05:20.560 --> 00:05:22.890
I'd rather go to the netherworld with you.

00:05:23.010 --> 00:05:25.210
Anyway, you're not allowed to leave me.

00:05:35.490 --> 00:05:37.350
How long have I been teaching you?

00:05:37.400 --> 00:05:39.290
Why are you still so stubborn?

00:05:39.409 --> 00:05:40.610
A leopard

00:05:40.790 --> 00:05:42.190
cannot change its spots.

00:05:42.680 --> 00:05:43.820
So you're despising me now?

00:05:43.820 --> 00:05:45.170
How would I despise you, Five?

00:05:45.170 --> 00:05:46.650
I'm just joking.

00:05:46.950 --> 00:05:48.090
This joke of yours

00:05:48.740 --> 00:05:50.220
is really deadly to me.

00:05:50.850 --> 00:05:52.900
Your life has always belonged to me.

00:05:53.760 --> 00:05:54.820
However,

00:05:55.780 --> 00:05:56.930
besides your life,

00:05:57.340 --> 00:05:58.870
I also want something else.

00:06:00.130 --> 00:06:02.130
Since you became the emperor,

00:06:02.370 --> 00:06:04.660
