outside the palace?

00:06:09.250 --> 00:06:10.010
No.

00:06:10.480 --> 00:06:12.130
You haven't fully recovered yet.

00:06:12.130 --> 00:06:13.810
I'm fine now.

00:06:13.840 --> 00:06:15.690
Keeping me confined
won't help me get better.

00:06:15.690 --> 00:06:16.840
The answer is still no.

00:06:16.840 --> 00:06:18.110
The weather will be bad tomorrow.

00:06:18.110 --> 00:06:19.670
How can you know whether

00:06:19.720 --> 00:06:21.040
tomorrow's weather will be fine or not?

00:06:21.040 --> 00:06:22.120
In brief, for the foreseeable future,

00:06:22.120 --> 00:06:23.850
