00:10:33.930 --> 00:10:35.510
I've experienced

00:10:36.210 --> 00:10:38.190
the same lifetime twice.

00:10:39.090 --> 00:10:41.060
This is my second life now.

00:10:41.480 --> 00:10:42.700
In my previous life,

00:10:43.120 --> 00:10:46.110
during the Lantern Festival
in the 28th year of Tianchen,

00:10:46.110 --> 00:10:49.510
my father was framed by Ding Huairen
and put into prison.

00:10:49.610 --> 00:10:52.750
