00:11:10.610 --> 00:11:12.090
and I died because of that.

00:11:23.900 --> 00:11:25.860
No wonder when you first met me,

00:11:25.920 --> 00:11:28.550
you used those little tricks
to bully me and vent your anger.

00:11:28.550 --> 00:11:30.380
