00:11:38.150 --> 00:11:39.720
and that was all my fault.

00:11:41.360 --> 00:11:42.330
Five.

00:11:43.030 --> 00:11:45.020
I know you like how I'm

00:11:45.390 --> 00:11:47.290
so enterprising

00:11:47.360 --> 00:11:49.050
and capable.

00:11:49.390 --> 00:11:52.030
But I wasn't like that at first.

00:11:52.670 --> 00:11:53.760
At that time,

00:11:54.030 --> 00:11:55.980
